package: NotesOverlay
author: Tony Lyons
version: 1.0
rv: 3.0
requires: ''

modes:
  - file: NotesOverlay
    load: immediate

description: |
  Review notes overlay plugin for OpenRV.
  Adds Review > Add Note menu for adding text annotations to frames.
  Notes are rendered as white text with black outline for readability.
  Notes persist in RVPaint node properties (survives session save/autosave).
